title: 053 - Zito Has A Prince Albert?!
description: On today's show, the guys discuss baby's having more bones than adult humans and how you can actually kind of shape them if you see fit, they look at the fast food places that have visited most during quarantine, go through the POD FOD (Folder of Death) which includes a few #PodFacts, what day officially starts the week, Big Motor makes a startling confession, and much more. This one is a good time. Enjoy.
